sequenceDiagram
    autonumber

    participant U as User
    participant FE as Frontend (Browser / Ajax)
    participant API as Backend REST API
    participant SS as Product Sorting Service
    participant DB as Database

    U->>FE: Select sorting option (Price Low → High)

    FE->>API: GET /api/products?sortBy=price&sortDir=asc&page=0&size=12

    API->>SS: sortProducts(sortBy,sortDir,page,size)

    SS->>DB: SELECT * FROM PRODUCTS\nORDER BY price ASC\nLIMIT page,size
    DB-->>SS: sorted products

    SS->>DB: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM PRODUCTS
    DB-->>SS: totalElements

    SS-->>API: ProductPage

    API-->>FE: ApiResponse<ProductPage>

    FE-->>U: Display sorted product grid